    sweetwater.com

    Description

    Sweetwater is an American musical instrument retailer. Based in Fort Wayne, Indiana, Sweetwater is the largest online retailer of musical instruments and pro audio equipment in the United States. Wikipedia
    Customer service: 1 (800) 222-4700
    Type of business: Corporation
    Revenue: 1.57 billion USD (2022)
    Founded: 1979, Fort Wayne, IN
    Founder: Chuck Surack
    Headquarters: Fort Wayne, IN
    Number of employees: 2,300
